{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, we pose the following secondary research questions:",
    "• SRQ1: What types of positive or negative, direct or indirect societal impact are observed?",
    "• SRQ2: What kinds of mechanisms produce them?",
    "• SRQ3: What specific enabling and/or inhibiting factors (drivers and barriers) are associated with these impacts?",
    "• SRQ4: What knowledge gaps emerge from this analysis?"
  ]
}